import React from 'react'
import { LoginSignUpWrapper, TitleText, FormContainer, Login, Signup,
    SliderTab, SlideControls, Field, PassLink, SignUpLink, ButtonLayer,
    FieldInput, Button, Title, FormInner, InnerForm, LinkPass, LinkSignUp,
    FullContainer} from './LoginSignUpElements'

const LoginSignUp = () => {
  return (
    <FullContainer>
        <LoginSignUpWrapper>
            <TitleText>
                <Title>
                    <Login>
                        Login Form
                    </Login>
                    <Signup>
                        Signup Form
                    </Signup>
                </Title>
            </TitleText>
            <FormContainer>
                <SlideControls>
                    <input type="radio" style={{display:'none'}} name="slide" id="login" checked />
                    <input type="radio" style={{display:'none'}} name="slide" id="signup" />
                    <Login for="login">Login</Login>
                    <Signup for="signup">Signup</Signup>
                    <SliderTab></SliderTab>
                </SlideControls>
                <FormInner>
                    <InnerForm action="#" class="login">
                        <Field>
                            <FieldInput type="text" placeholder="Email Address" required />
                        </Field>
                        <Field>
                            <FieldInput type="password" placeholder="Password" required />
                        </Field>
                        <PassLink>
                            <LinkPass href="google.com">Forgot password?</LinkPass>
                        </PassLink>
                        <Field>
                            <Button>
                                <ButtonLayer></ButtonLayer>
                                <FieldInput type="submit" value="Login"></FieldInput>
                            </Button>
                        </Field>
                        <SignUpLink>
                            Not a member? <LinkSignUp href="google.com">Signup now</LinkSignUp>
                        </SignUpLink>
                    </InnerForm>
                    <InnerForm action="#" class="signup">
                        <Field>
                            <FieldInput type="text" placeholder="Email Address" required />
                        </Field>
                        <Field>
                            <FieldInput type="password" placeholder="Password" required />
                        </Field>
                        <Field>
                            <FieldInput type="password" placeholder="Confirm password" required />
                        </Field>
                        <Field>
                            <Button>
                                <ButtonLayer></ButtonLayer>
                                <FieldInput type="submit" value="Signup"></FieldInput>
                            </Button>
                        </Field>
                    </InnerForm>
                </FormInner>
            </FormContainer>
        </LoginSignUpWrapper>
    </FullContainer>
  );
};

export default LoginSignUp;
